data.description: Discover the expansive and well-designed floor plan with exquisite touches, nested in a sought-after community. Revel in a wealth of upgrades, including a smart home system, luxurious plank flooring, custom blinds, finished back patio featuring turf and pavers, Rest easy with the convenience of two car garage where you can enter the unit on the first level, where a master bedroom/bath awaits. The main living area has a spacious layout and electric fireplace. Gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, ample cabinet space with a pantry for additional storage, all connecting to the open living area for an open floor plan thats great for entertaining. Soon the community is to unveil a delightful pool along with the park area, enhancing the overall experience. The properties prime location places it in close proximity to restaurants, grocery, shopping and the official Olympic Training Center, along side the great schools for the children, making it an idea place to call home. Act swiftly for this exceptional property is bound to be in high demand.Fridge, washer & dryer does not convey but negotiable. Pool is not yet built out, once completed, HOA will see an increase of approximately $12.36.
